units.approachToLearning:
This unit enhances learning through the following means:

•	Three hours of detailed lectures each week; theory, examples and various ideas are presented to the student;
•	A one hour tutorial each week; discussion of exercises;
•	Feedback on assignments and class tests, with solutions presented in vUWS for the student to review.

Furthermore,  During the semester, students will prepare and present a solution to a tutorial question on the whiteboard in the class. This will help them to practice their presentation skills, as well as acquiring a deeper understanding of the subject. The Assignment is designed to provide an opportunity for solving problems without the pressure of time, to give feedback about students progress, and most importantly to help students learn the content of the unit.

